<subSubSection id="79DA6524362BFC09C482D8A4FB9CB404" pageId="18" pageNumber="383" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="317F36AF362BFC09C482D8A4FB9CB404" blockId="18.[178,1085,1435,1545]" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">
<taxonomicName id="F6C04D2C362BFC09C482D8A4FEB4B7BC" authorityName="MANNERHEIM" authorityYear="1830" box="[178,283,1435,1457]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Oxypoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="397" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Sphenoma">
<emphasis id="03B4EABD362BFC09C482D8A4FEB4B7BC" box="[178,283,1435,1457]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">Sphenoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was previously represented in the Palaearctic region by eighteen species (
<bibRefCitation id="55514B5E362BFC09C489D887FEEBB7C3" author="ASSING V" box="[185,324,1464,1486]" pageId="18" pageNumber="383" pagination="1307 - 1315" refId="ref20031" refString="ASSING V. (2009): On some Oxypoda species of the subgenus Sphenoma MANNERHEIM (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Linzer biologische Beitrage 41 (2): 1307 - 1315." type="journal article" year="2009">ASSING 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="55514B5E362BFC09C560D887FE28B7C3" author="ASSING V" box="[336,391,1464,1486]" pageId="18" pageNumber="383" pagination="137 - 183" refId="ref20154" refString="ASSING V. (2011): On the Staphylinidae (Coleoptera) of Iran. II. New species and additional records, with special reference to the Paederinae, Xantholinini, and Aleocharinae. - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A, Neue Serie 4: 137 - 183." type="journal article" year="2011">2011</bibRefCitation>
). The subgenus is poorly defined and the subgeneric affiliations of several species currently attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="F6C04D2C362BFC09C669D8E9FD6DB7E1" authorityName="MANNERHEIM" authorityYear="1830" box="[601,706,1494,1516]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Oxypoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="397" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Sphenoma">
<emphasis id="03B4EABD362BFC09C669D8E9FD6DB7E1" box="[601,706,1494,1516]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">Sphenoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have not been revised. Only one 
<taxonomicName id="F6C04D2C362BFC09C482D8CCFEA2B404" authority="MANNERHEIM" authorityName="MANNERHEIM" authorityYear="1830" box="[178,269,1523,1545]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Oxypoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="383" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="03B4EABD362BFC09C482D8CCFEA2B404" box="[178,269,1523,1545]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">Oxypoda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species, 
<taxonomicName id="F6C04D2C362BFC09C559D8CBFD53B404" authority="ASSING 2009" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2009" box="[361,764,1523,1545]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Oxypoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="383" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kirghisica" subGenus="Sphenoma">
<emphasis id="03B4EABD362BFC09C559D8CBFED4B404" box="[361,379,1524,1545]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">O</emphasis>
. (
<emphasis id="03B4EABD362BFC09C5A1D8CCFE55B404" box="[401,506,1523,1545]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">Sphenoma</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="03B4EABD362BFC09C639D8CCFDC1B404" box="[521,622,1523,1545]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">kirghisica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="55514B5E362BFC09C644D8CCFD53B404" author="ASSING V" box="[628,764,1523,1545]" pageId="18" pageNumber="383" pagination="1307 - 1315" refId="ref20031" refString="ASSING V. (2009): On some Oxypoda species of the subgenus Sphenoma MANNERHEIM (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Linzer biologische Beitrage 41 (2): 1307 - 1315." type="journal article" year="2009">ASSING 2009</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, was known from 
<collectingCountry id="49D7763F362BFC09C786D8CBFB81B404" box="[950,1070,1524,1545]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="18" pageNumber="383">Kyrgyzstan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
